                <h1>What Does TED Stand For? Discover Its Meaning</h1>
                <p>TED stands for Technology, Entertainment, and Design. Founded in 1984, TED began as a conference bringing together these three fields. Today, it has evolved into a global platform where thought leaders share innovative ideas through TED Talks, fostering inspiration and knowledge exchange worldwide.</p>
